Cheat Sheet for Long Positions

If You See... Action
Price > VWAP, RSI > 50, MFI > 50, all rising ✅ STRONG BUY (Standard Trade)
Price > VWAP, RSI rising from <30, MFI rising ⚠️ BOUNCE BUY (Advanced Trade)
Price < VWAP ❌ No long
RSI > 70 and falling ❌ Wait for pullback
MFI < 30 and falling ❌ Capitulation, wait
RSI > 50 but MFI < 40 ⚠️ Divergence (price up, no volume)

---

Bottom Line

Indicator Ideal for Long What to Watch
VWAP Price > VWAP Crossing above VWAP = buy signal
RSI 50-70 and rising Recovery from oversold = bounce
MFI > 50 and rising Confirms volume supports the move

Best signal: All three aligned (price > VWAP, RSI > 50 and rising, MFI > 50 and rising)

Second best: Bounce setup (RSI recovering from <30, price reclaiming VWAP, MFI turning up)
